"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-06-25-no-french-fries-lots-lentils-paris-olympic-athletes\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP)- There will be no French fries but plenty of lentils offered to athletes attending the Paris Olympics, with organisers unveiling their food offering on Tuesday that combines eco-minded recipes with French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French fries\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\"}, {\"begin\": 218, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5512813011317673, \"rank\": 0.8109085463167549, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AFP)-\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 20}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"lentils\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 84, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"their food offering\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 168}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 179}, {\"ngram\": \"eco-minded recipes\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The giant 3,300-seat restaurant at the Paris Olympic village, which will welcome athletes next month, was given its first test-run on Tuesday by a hungry crowd of sports figures, officials and journalists.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.6033716567994235e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The giant 3,300-seat restaurant\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"a hungry crowd\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"sports figures\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Based in a vast former power station, the food hall includes six different dining areas offering meals from around the globe, with half of the 50 dishes available each day being 100 percent vegetarian.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a vast former power station\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the food hall\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"six different dining areas\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"meals\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50 dishes\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People are going to meet here in France, with its culture, its heritage but also its gastronomy and so there are expectations,\\\" chief Paris 2024 organiser Tony Estanguet told reporters.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999997586856189, \"rank\": 2.304696185783239e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.270597293199788e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"its culture\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"its heritage\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"its gastronomy\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although many athletes would stick to their usual nutrition before competing, they will also be offered the chance to discover France's famed food, with several Michelin-starred chefs taken on as advisors.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999997586856189, \"rank\": 2.304696185783239e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin-starred\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"their usual nutrition\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"advisors\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have allowed ourselves to put French gastronomy in pride of place so that curious athletes from around the world can try French culinary excellence,\\\" Estanguet added.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5512813011317673, \"rank\": 0.8109085463167549, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5512813011317673, \"rank\": 0.8109085463167549, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"curious athletes\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The giant warm-food buffets will not include French fries, however.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French fries\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The giant warm-food buffets\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McDonalds, a long-time Olympics sponsor, had its own fast-food restaurant in the Olympic village until the Rio Olympics in 2016, but athletes wanting a hit of junk food will have to look elsewhere in Paris.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 5.170415351595442e-13, \"text\": \"Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.6033716567994235e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McDonalds\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-time Olympics sponsor\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"its own fast-food restaurant\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"a hit\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"junk food\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For technical reasons, we can not offer fries,\\\" said Estelle Lamotte, deputy director of village catering at food group Sodexo, told reporters.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estelle_Getty\", \"score\": 0.999872042653774, \"rank\": 0.0001279737163715987, \"text\": \"Estelle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estelle_Getty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estelle_Getty\"}, {\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"technical reasons\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"fries\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"deputy director\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"village\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She explained deep-fat fryers were not allowed in the temporary kitchens at the site, which is usually used as a film studio.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deep-fat fryers\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"the temporary kitchens\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"a film studio\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gregoire Bechu, head of sustainable food at the Paris organising committee, stressed the quality of the \\\"delicious\\\" lentil dal recipe that has been developed for athletes.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.6033716567994235e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gregoire Bechu\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable food\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"delicious\\\" lentil dal recipe\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the major commitments by Paris 2024 was offering vegetarian meals in order to halve the carbon footprint of each meal on average,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.270597293199788e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the major commitments\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"vegetarian meals\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"the carbon footprint\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"each meal\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We wanted vegetarian meals everywhere.\\\"\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"vegetarian meals\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At sports venues, 60 percent of food offered to fans will be vegetarian and the temporary stadium hosting skateboarding, BMX and breakdancing at the Place de la Concorde in central Paris will be entirely meat-free.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999989402427831, \"rank\": 6.942836815505227e-07, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 2278, \"end\": 2298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2586295780361254e-15, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.6033716567994235e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports venues\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"60 percent\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the temporary stadium hosting skateboarding\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a further bid to lower carbon emissions, only two of the six restaurant areas at the village will be air-conditioned, with the rest in outdoor courtyards sheltered by fabric sun shades and ventilated with overhead fans.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a further bid\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon emissions\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"the six restaurant areas\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"outdoor courtyards\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"fabric sun\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"overhead fans\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tuesday's test event, held under fierce sunshine and in 27C (80F) heat, saw some people visibly sweating.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tuesday's test event\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"fierce sunshine\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"27C (80F) heat\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we have found a good compromise between offering the right temperature but also reducing our carbon emissions,\\\" Estanguet said.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good compromise\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the right temperature\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"our carbon emissions\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2794}, {\"ngram\": \"Estanguet\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's one of the main challenges of the Paris 2024 edition.\\\"\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main challenges\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 edition\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a break from Olympic tradition, the 2,800 apartments at the village do not come with air-conditioning as standard.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic tradition\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2,800 apartments\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"air-conditioning\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"standard\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But many Olympic teams have decided to install portable coolers at their own cost.\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many Olympic teams\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"portable coolers\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3057}, {\"ngram\": \"their own cost\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris has suffered a series of record heatwaves in recent years with temperatures peaking above 40C in July and August, but 2024 has so far been wet and cool.\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3078, \"end\": 3083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.6033716567994235e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3105}, {\"ngram\": \"record heatwaves\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"temperatures\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3159}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics run from July 26-August 11 followed by the Paralympics August 28-September 8.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3256}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"-August\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics August\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags: HOUSE RULES Comments are closed.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES Comments\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3362}]}]}"